1
00:00:03,260 --> 00:00:04,170
Changyan,

2
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:05,360
you're cheating.

3
00:00:06,630 --> 00:00:08,590
We use the affairs of the state
as our chessboard,

4
00:00:08,590 --> 00:00:10,830
and officials and commoners
as pieces in our game.

5
00:00:10,830 --> 00:00:12,790
You deliberately set a trap to lure me in.

6
00:00:12,790 --> 00:00:14,430
You can do this on the chessboard,

7
00:00:14,430 --> 00:00:15,800
but would you also

8
00:00:16,190 --> 00:00:17,790
stake yourself in the court?

9
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:22,390
If I were to govern the court one day,

10
00:00:22,390 --> 00:00:23,640
I would prioritize the state

11
00:00:23,640 --> 00:00:24,640
above the throne.

12
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:26,700
Even if I must bear infamy,

13
00:00:27,230 --> 00:00:29,430
I will prove my principles with my life.

14
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:11,300
[Luminosity Behind The Palace]

15
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,000
My Lady.

16
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,150
My Lady.

17
00:01:24,310 --> 00:01:25,640
My Lady, you're finally awake.

18
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,870
I heard that the Marquis...

19
00:01:26,870 --> 00:01:28,950
failed to provide reinforcements in time,

20
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,510
causing heavy casualties for the army.

21
00:01:30,510 --> 00:01:31,710
He's been imprisoned

22
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,180
and might be executed.

23
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,130
What did you say?

24
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:36,960
No.

25
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,380
I must see His Majesty.

26
00:01:39,950 --> 00:01:40,810
My Lady.

27
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:41,560
Wan,

28
00:01:41,789 --> 00:01:43,120
help me change quickly.

29
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:46,710
[Ningzheng Hall]

30
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:47,800
Your Majesty,

31
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,150
my brother, Marquis Jingyuan,
has led troops for years,

32
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:51,310
loyal to Dacang,

33
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,590
giving everything for it.

34
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:54,400
How could he have delayed the battle?

35
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,930
There must be more to this.

36
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,800
I hope Your Majesty
will investigate thoroughly.

37
00:01:59,789 --> 00:02:00,950
Court affairs

38
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,550
are none of your concern.

39
00:02:11,090 --> 00:02:12,350
Your Majesty once said

40
00:02:14,330 --> 00:02:17,060
that if the court itself
cannot act righteously,

41
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,070
how can it

42
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,930
bring justice to the world?

43
00:02:25,610 --> 00:02:26,410
Your Majesty,

44
00:02:26,670 --> 00:02:27,410
noble clans have
seized the common people's land.

45
00:02:27,410 --> 00:02:28,890
[Map of the Nine States]

46
00:02:28,890 --> 00:02:30,890
Today we must speak out for justice.

47
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,520
Mother,

48
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,240
this matter must
be thoroughly investigated.

49
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,579
If the court itself
cannot act righteously,

50
00:02:37,579 --> 00:02:39,640
how can it bring justice to the world?

51
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:48,950
Su Leyu,

52
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:54,160
you're the eldest miss of the Su family.

53
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:55,940
You should have
recused yourself from this case,

54
00:02:55,940 --> 00:02:56,910
don't you understand?

55
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:58,570
I'm indeed from the Su family,

56
00:02:59,590 --> 00:03:01,390
but I'm also a citizen of Dacang.

57
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:03,370
I humbly request Your Majesty

58
00:03:04,050 --> 00:03:05,470
to allow me to leave the palace

59
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:06,670
to uncover the truth.

60
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:09,680
Request?

61
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:14,290
By what authority
do you make requests of me?

62
00:03:16,130 --> 00:03:17,850
The late empress taught me:

63
00:03:18,410 --> 00:03:19,940
Better to be shattered jade

64
00:03:20,329 --> 00:03:21,460
than an intact tile.

65
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,079
Your Majesty,

66
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:31,550
this matter concerns the state,

67
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,500
and there must be an explanation.

68
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:38,130
If Your Majesty forces me into marriage,

69
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,780
I cannot obey.

70
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,120
But I beg Your Majesty

71
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,820
to prioritize the welfare of the state

72
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:44,150
and grant me permission

73
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,090
to investigate the truth.

74
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,340
Afterward,

75
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,440
I will atone for my sins with my life.

76
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:07,130
Since you've already claimed

77
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:09,080
that I act without integrity,

78
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,180
then why do you

79
00:04:12,210 --> 00:04:14,410
come begging to me, a supposed usurper?

80
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,750
I spoke out of turn,

81
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,400
and deserve to die for it.

82
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:36,570
All I ask is a few days,

83
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:38,630
after which I will uncover the truth

84
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,270
and...

85
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:45,290
accept whatever punishment
Your Majesty deems fit.

86
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:49,070
But,

87
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,420
what if you fail to uncover the truth?

88
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:55,480
Our Su family

89
00:04:56,710 --> 00:04:58,909
controls the military power of Dacang,

90
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:02,300
and my brother inherits
the title of Marquis Jingyuan.

91
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,880
If my brother truly delayed the battle,

92
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,320
then I, Su Leyu,

93
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:10,070
would be ashamed to face the late empress,

94
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:12,040
nor face the ancestors of Dacang.

95
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,100
I would willingly join my brother

96
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,200
in beheading ourselves,

97
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:23,160
to honor the souls of
Dacang's fallen soldiers.

98
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,630
Are you threatening me with your life?

99
00:05:30,110 --> 00:05:31,450
How can your single life

100
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:34,240
compare to tens of thousands
of Dacang soldiers?

101
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,140
Forget about that.

102
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:57,800
I...

103
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,960
forbid it.

104
00:06:16,090 --> 00:06:19,640
[Ever-growing Radiance]

105
00:06:35,659 --> 00:06:36,460
Your Majesty,

106
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:38,980
since you won't let me leave the palace,

107
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:40,240
I'll have to sneak out.

108
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:43,520
These square walls may confine you,

109
00:06:43,990 --> 00:06:45,250
but they can't hold me.

110
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,280
I will uncover the truth,

111
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:50,290
for my brother,

112
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:51,800
and for

113
00:06:52,670 --> 00:06:52,740
Dacang.

114
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:56,590
[Central Palace Gate]

115
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:00,600
[Supreme Court]

116
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,190
Brother.

117
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,000
Leyu.

118
00:07:02,510 --> 00:07:04,090
They haven't tortured you, have they?

119
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:04,600
No.

120
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,510
You sneaked out of the palace again?

121
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,830
The court is in turmoil now.

122
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:08,830
You must not get involved

123
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:09,870
in these political affairs.

124
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:11,190
Now that you're imprisoned,

125
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:12,720
how can I just stand by and do nothing?

126
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,680
The noble families behind
the Justice Bureau and Ministry of Justice

127
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,800
surely want to see
our marquis household fall.

128
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,620
Do you really expect

129
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:18,390
them to give us

130
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:19,510
a fair judgment?

131
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:21,440
Brother,

132
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,040
tell me everything

133
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,240
that happened to you.

134
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,990
Once I understand the situation,

135
00:07:25,990 --> 00:07:27,680
when His Majesty asks about it,

136
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,080
I'll know how to respond.

137
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,760
Have you heard of

138
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,090
"Ghost Soldiers Passing"?

139
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:37,270
Ghost Soldiers Passing?

140
00:07:38,730 --> 00:07:41,270
[Ever-growing Radiance]

141
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,070
Your Majesty,

142
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:44,000
Minister of Justice Wang Zhan

143
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:45,720
and Supreme Court Chief Feng Linyu

144
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,540
request an audience outside the hall.

145
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:49,540
Is it about Marquis Jingyuan again?

146
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,780
Yes, Your Majesty.

147
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,040
Rumors spread since Marquis Jingyuan's held

148
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,170
at the Supreme Court

149
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:55,120
awaiting trial.

150
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,480
They don't know

151
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,950
how to proceed,

152
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,750
and seek Your Majesty's word.

153
00:08:01,070 --> 00:08:03,280
I intend to take Su Leyu as my consort.

154
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:05,390
These aristocratic families

155
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:06,680
fear that the Su family's military power

156
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,920
will become mine.

157
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:11,040
So they want me
to investigate Su Wencheng myself.

158
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:11,750
That way,

159
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:14,000
the Su family would
lose their military authority,

160
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,800
and these families
could seize it for themselves.

161
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:19,260
They're forcing my hand.

162
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,290
Then I shall tell them

163
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,980
that Your Majesty
has retired for the night

164
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:24,040
and send them away.

165
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:24,850
No.

166
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,390
These noble families

167
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:28,120
have finally shown their true colors.

168
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,190
Rather than playing along,

169
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:31,250
I'll turn their scheme against them.

170
00:08:31,430 --> 00:08:32,600
Go tell them

171
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:34,049
to conduct the trial as they should,

172
00:08:34,049 --> 00:08:35,960
with whoever should preside over it.

173
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,669
Aren't the laws of Dacang

174
00:08:36,669 --> 00:08:37,870
clear enough?

175
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,500
Yes, Your Majesty.

176
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,200
What else?

177
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,510
Supreme Court Chief Feng

178
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,840
mentioned something interesting to me.

179
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,570
He said that in the prison of the Court,

180
00:08:49,570 --> 00:08:50,390
he saw a

181
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:52,840
servant girl from
the Marquis Jingyuan's household

182
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,320
who looks exactly

183
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,080
like Miss Su.

184
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,320
Your Majesty,

185
00:08:56,490 --> 00:08:58,650
isn't that quite a coincidence?

186
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,760
When did this happen?

187
00:09:01,990 --> 00:09:03,150
Two hours ago.

188
00:09:28,090 --> 00:09:29,550
Greetings, Your Majesty.

189
00:09:35,070 --> 00:09:37,070
I assume Your Majesty already knew.

190
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:39,360
You left the palace

191
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:42,330
without permission
and trespassed into the prison.

192
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:44,060
I could have you imprisoned

193
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:45,090
along with Su Wencheng.

194
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:45,890
Your Majesty,

195
00:09:46,990 --> 00:09:48,240
do you truly believe my brother

196
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,460
would delay the battle?

197
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:50,200
Whatever I believe,

198
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:50,910
it's no excuse

199
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:52,310
for your defiance.

200
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:54,340
I only want to save my brother.

201
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,220
But just because I'm from the Su family,

202
00:09:57,220 --> 00:09:58,150
must I be a piece

203
00:09:58,150 --> 00:10:00,210
dragged in your power struggle game?

204
00:10:03,990 --> 00:10:06,050
We were already on the board long ago.

205
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,680
There was no "dragging you in."

206
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:14,570
I remember
when Your Majesty once faced the game

207
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:16,320
and made that bold promise

208
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,920
to prove your path
even at the cost of your life.

209
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,030
But now as the player,

210
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:24,050
both black and white pieces
serve your purpose.

211
00:10:24,510 --> 00:10:25,440
Yet Your Majesty

212
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:29,000
has been blinded by these colors.

213
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,590
I can overlook

214
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:43,270
your unauthorized
departure from the palace.

215
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:45,000
Whatever you wish
to uncover in the future,

216
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,460
I can also turn a blind eye.

217
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:49,710
You asked for a few days,

218
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,050
and I've granted them.

219
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,510
But after that,

220
00:10:53,130 --> 00:10:54,660
regardless of the outcome,

221
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,560
the conferment ceremony

222
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,370
will proceed as scheduled.

223
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,320
I forbid you to die.

224
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,450
Your Majesty means...?

225
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:04,640
Exactly what I said.

226
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:16,360
Su Leyu,

227
00:11:19,850 --> 00:11:21,440
you only have a few days.

228
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:40,160
Brother,

229
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:42,560
what's Ghost Soldiers Passing all about?

230
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,280
That night,

231
00:11:43,490 --> 00:11:44,960
I was leading my troops forward,

232
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,930
when we approached Changding Bridge,

233
00:11:46,930 --> 00:11:48,270
a thick fog suddenly appeared,

234
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:50,400
and I got separated from the main army.

235
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:52,440
Then I saw them.

236
00:12:01,210 --> 00:12:03,270
I followed the ghost soldiers' trail

237
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:04,740
to Changding Bridge.

238
00:12:07,690 --> 00:12:08,550
To my surprise,

239
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,170
the bridge had collapsed.

240
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,620
Under the collapsed bridge,

241
00:12:13,710 --> 00:12:16,040
there was a message
hidden in a fish belly.

242
00:12:23,260 --> 00:12:23,380
[Smashing jade in fury, kill the king to
usurp the throne. Ghost soldiers descend.]

243
00:12:23,380 --> 00:12:24,900
Smashing jade in fury,

244
00:12:24,930 --> 00:12:26,420
kill the king to usurp the throne.

245
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:26,510
[Heaven shaken,
Dacang doomed to fall by its hand.]

246
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:27,910
Ghost soldiers descend.

247
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:28,750
Dacang

248
00:12:29,190 --> 00:12:30,650
doomed to fall by its hand.

249
00:12:32,050 --> 00:12:33,310
Smashing jade in fury?

250
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:36,580
You ungrateful son!

251
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:39,650
What happened next?

252
00:12:40,010 --> 00:12:41,720
After I found my scattered troops,

253
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,120
I had to find another route,

254
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,200
forced to take a detour
to the Northern Territory.

255
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,800
The delay cost us the battle.

256
00:12:46,810 --> 00:12:48,150
The collapsed bridge,

257
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:49,510
the message in a fish's belly,

258
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:50,910
Ghost Soldiers Passing,

259
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,760
all these strange omens

260
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,700
somehow point to His Majesty.

261
00:12:55,150 --> 00:12:56,280
It seems this matter

262
00:12:56,970 --> 00:12:58,970
isn't just targeting the Su family,

263
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,600
but perhaps aims to take down

264
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:03,130
both our family
and His Majesty in one stroke.

265
00:13:03,310 --> 00:13:04,330
Time is short.

266
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,670
We need to find clues

267
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,800
in the Changding Bridge case quickly.

268
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:08,690
Your Majesty,

269
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,720
Marquis Jingyuan has
delayed military operations,

270
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:10,960
causing our soldiers to die in battle,

271
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,960
[Taiji Palace]

272
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,510
and rumors of the fish-belly message

273
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,510
are spreading wildly.

274
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,210
I believe

275
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:17,790
all of this is Marquis Jingyuan's fault,

276
00:13:17,790 --> 00:13:19,790
and he should be convicted immediately.

277
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:20,590
Your Majesty,

278
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:22,750
Lord Xi speaks the truth.

279
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,630
If Your Majesty hesitates because

280
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:26,960
the Marquis bears the Su surname,

281
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:27,960
I'm afraid it will

282
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:30,200
disappoint your people's heart.

283
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,400
Your Majesty,

284
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:34,050
I must speak even at the risk of my life.

285
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:36,270
