368
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:24,110
to weaken the Su family's power.

369
00:18:27,310 --> 00:18:28,570
No matter what the Qin,

370
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,050
Xi, or Wang families

371
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,790
have said or done,

372
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:33,170
our Su family

373
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:35,220
